messages.content: Analyze the wandb project https://wandb.ai/mluo/deepscaler-1.5b?nw=nwusermluo, using the experiment logs to analyze which experiment results should be chosen if we want a model that provides the shortest answers to questions. Please record the entropy_loss, clip_ratio, and response_length_mean for this experiment from step 0, at intervals of every 100 steps, into the workspace file shortest_length_experiment.csv.

function.name: wandb-query_wandb_tool
function.arguments: {"query":"query ProjectInfo($entity: String!, $project: String!) { project(name: $project, entityName: $entity) { id name entityName description runCount } }","variables":{"entity":"mluo","project":"deepscaler-1.5b"}}

function.name: wandb-query_wandb_tool
function.arguments: {"query":"query GetRuns($entity: String!, $project: String!, $limit: Int) { project(name: $project, entityName: $entity) { runs(first: $limit, order: \"-createdAt\") { edges { node { id name displayName createdAt summaryMetrics historyKeys } } pageInfo { endCursor hasNextPage } } } }","variables":{"entity":"mluo","project":"deepscaler-1.5b","limit":20},"max_items":100}

function.name: wandb-query_wandb_tool
function.arguments: {"query":"query RunHistorySampled($entity: String!, $project: String!, $runId: String!, $specs: [JSONString!]!) { project(name: $project, entityName: $entity) { run(name: $runId) { id name displayName sampledHistory(specs: $specs) } } }","variables":{"entity":"mluo","project":"deepscaler-1.5b","runId":"iklki6k0","specs":["{\"keys\": [\"_step\", \"actor/entropy_loss\", \"response_length/clip_ratio\", \"response_length/mean\"]}"]},"max_items":100}

function.name: wandb-query_wandb_tool
function.arguments: {"query":"query RunFiles($entity: String!, $project: String!, $runId: String!, $limit: Int) { project(name: $project, entityName: $entity) { run(name: $runId) { id name displayName files(first: $limit) { edges { node { name url } } pageInfo { endCursor hasNextPage } } } } }","variables":{"entity":"mluo","project":"deepscaler-1.5b","runId":"iklki6k0","limit":200},"max_items":100}

function.name: wandb-query_wandb_tool
function.arguments: {"query":"query RunHistorySampled($entity: String!, $project: String!, $runId: String!, $specs: [JSONString!]!) { project(name: $project, entityName: $entity) { run(name: $runId) { id name displayName sampledHistory(specs: $specs) } } }","variables":{"entity":"mluo","project":"deepscaler-1.5b","runId":"iklki6k0","specs":["{\"keys\": [\"actor/entropy_loss\", \"response_length/clip_ratio\", \"response_length/mean\"]}"]},"max_items":100}

function.name: wandb-query_wandb_tool
function.arguments: {"query":"query RunHistorySampled($entity: String!, $project: String!, $runId: String!, $specs: [JSONString!]!) { project(name: $project, entityName: $entity) { run(name: $runId) { id name displayName historyLineCount sampledHistory(specs: $specs) } } }","variables":{"entity":"mluo","project":"deepscaler-1.5b","runId":"iklki6k0","specs":["{\"keys\": [\"_step\", \"actor/entropy_loss\", \"response_length/clip_ratio\", \"response_length/mean\"], \"samples\": 10000}"]},"max_items":100}

messages.content:
Done.

Summary analysis:
- Compared runs in mluo/deepscaler-1.5b using response_length/mean:
  - deepscaler-1.5b-24k: ~5371.8
  - deepscaler-1.5b-16k: ~5163.9
  - deepscaler-1.5b-8k: ~4537.9
  - deepscaler-1.5b-4k-ablation: ~2380.9
  - deepscaler-1.5b-2k-ablation: ~1345.3

Selection:
- The run “deepscaler-1.5b-2k-ablation” (run id: iklki6k0) has by far the shortest responses and is the best choice if the goal is minimal answer length.

CSV created:
- File: /workspace/dumps/workspace/shortest_length_experiment.csv
- Contents (entropy_loss, clip_ratio [response_length/clip_ratio], response_length_mean [response_length/mean]) at steps 0, 100, 200, 300, 400:
